  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK284">
<l>kaḷaviṉkaṭ kaṉṟiya kātal viḷaiviṉkaṇ</l>
<l>vīyā viḻuman tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The eager desire of defrauding others will, when it brings forth its fruit, produce undying sorrow.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
